  "text": "The cost criteria are well known and it is easy to modify them to derive more suitable versions for evaluating the performance. It should be noted that the cost criteria above do not depend on the controller output, i.e., the control signal, at all. Thus a novel optimal control-like cost function is introduced that also applies for trajectory control. This function is presented in [CITATION_1] , and it will be referred as IERC (Integral of Weighted Sum of Square Error and Required Control Signal Error) criterion.",
  "correct_citation": {
